<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="systematic-adj">systematic <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌsɪstə'mætɪk/    美 /ˌsɪstə'mætɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有系统的；有计划步骤的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He knew that his success was almost entirely due to his assistant’s systematic hard work. 
他知道自己的成功几乎完全归功于助手有条不紊的努力工作。</p><footer>人教⑨ – 1</footer></div></div>